data.description: Welcome to 812 Kathie, a beautiful 4-bedroom home where comfort and style come together in over 2,000 square feet of living space. This wonderful property offers a delightful combination of modern amenities, ample living space, and a generous backyard, making it the perfect place to call home. One of the many enchanting features of this home is the captivating fireplace. Imagine relaxing around the crackling fire, creating cherished moments and memories. Whether you're looking to unwind after a long day or host intimate gatherings with friends, this fireplace is sure to be the heart of your home. Plus, new indoor and outdoor AC Unit will be installed December 4th. Contact your favorite broker for a tour today! Your dream home is closer than you think.
